article_text: We are pleased to introduce you to the winners of the 17th annual Miami Herald Business Plan Challenge. The winners’ circle contains concepts in healthcare, antiques, food, tech and social entrepreneurship. To rise to the top, winners had to make a strong case for how they planned to execute their business plan.
